dict.string: A Super Maze 3D Race Through Time Fun Game FREE

Race against the clock or challenge your friends head to head as you try to find your way through the maze. Collect diamonds and mystery items along the way. Randomly generated mazes mean it's never the same and always exciting. Unlock new levels and move from the past to the present then on to the future. Unlock additional characters and items as well!

Install Super Maze 3D today, and get all these great features:

- Universal for both iPhone and iPad.
- High quality 3D graphics for Retina displays and iPad.
- 2 player mode with Game Center integration.
- Play as 3 different characters.
- New maze every time!

**** Ranked #48 in Games/Strategy Category!

Cool Dog “Darby” needs to get to her doghouse with all of her bones – QUICKLY! And you won’t EVER run out of time to finish the game!
Never the same maze in any of the 3 levels of difficulty!

*** Was Top Puzzle Game in 13 Countries! Top Strategy Game in 21 Countries!***

OMG CUTE!!!!!!!!!!!! - Joey makes me laugh, hopping around like a kangaroo. Cute!

Outstanding! - Great graphics and game design! A++

One of the most unique maze style games yet! Fun and challenging with 30 levels! The higher the level, the more bad guys to avoid!

Little Joey has wandered away from Mama! He’s gone to collect gold for her but now you need to help him get home!

But watch out for the bad guys! Along the way, Joey could run into any of these creatures: a wonambi, dingos, a thylacine, marsupial lion, mean cats, wedge-tailed eagle, a crocodile or a big bad kangaroo complete with boxing gloves who could knock him out and steal his nuggets!

And that monkey! Just as Joey’s about to get a nugget, the monkey throws them somewhere else! Good grief!
 
So use the joystick to help Joey get safely home to Mama with lots of gold nuggets and bars!

Game Features:

-Puzzle and strategy combined!
-Adorable Joey, the little kangaroo 
-Fantastic graphics!
-Collect all gold bars and nugget to unlock the next levels
-Customize Joey 
-Challenge your skills in higher levels – more bad guys to avoid!
-Use the joystick for easy control
-Jump button helps Joey jump over the river or on to the crocodle’s back to move up and down the river.

The racing game that provides plenty of juicy fun and zany antics! You’ll be entertained for hours by this unique race which follows six loveable fruits through perilous turns and obstacle-ridden paths. Play as one of several quirky characters that are sure to satisfy your craving for fun…and fruit!

Adam Apple, Ben Blueberry, Cherie Cherry, and friends will roll onto your screen and you won’t be able to put them down! Dodge obstacles and collect the food and prizes in your path. If you like races with cars or bikes, you won’t find them here…this is mushy fruit! Loopy Fruits Race offers a truly unique experience!

If sabotage is your style, you’ll love this tricky little game. These ruthless little guys will do anything to get to the finish line; even if it means squashing their friends! Push obstacles in the way to win coins and other prizes, or for those of you who need instant gratification, buy coins from the shop! Either way, this whimsical racing game will really get your juices flowing!
Tap Ladder Insanity to the Moon - Fun, Family Skill Game for Adults & Children

How Many Ladders Can You Connect?

Try to reach for the moon by building your ladder piece by piece! Help Ted the brave bear and Cocoa the magical rabbit to get to the moon as quick as you can!

*** 3 Fun Modes of Play

Quick Game - see how high you can build up the ladder but when 3 pieces fall - game over! Each section built equals 1 point.

Score Attack - perfectly match the ladders and get 5 points! Slightly mismatched ladders only give you 2 points. Game over when 3 pieces fall.

Time Attack - you have 30 seconds to see how fast you can build a ladder!

But don't let the mysterious forest enchant you with its beautiful storybook graphics and magical music!

This physics based game will challenge you and delight people of all ages! Complete with intuitive controls that will get you playing as soon as you start the game!

Tiny Ninja Dash! GET READY TO BATTLE! It's a cold, windy winter day and you must get control of the bridge. You have joined forces with the white ninjas in an attempt to prevent the dark ninjas from crossing the bridge and getting to the other side.

You must try to knock the evil dark ninjas off the bridge with your throwing star. But it is a windy day and the wind will try and knock your throwing star off course. Aim carefully as you try and knock off as many as you can to WIN the battle for the bridge. Watch out for those ninjas disguised in the rice hats as it will take you TWO throws to knock them off. And of course make sure that you don't hit any of the white ninjas or you lose one life. Hit FIVE consecutive dark ninjas and you get one extra life. 

Compare your high score count with your other ninja friends in game center to see how you rank as a ninja warrior. A fun and addicting FPS (first person shooter) game that will make you come back for more!
Voters’ Revenge: Top Free Game for Whacking Politicians

No matter who you vote for you’ll love this game!

Voters’ Revenge is your chance to get your thumb (or your finger) on prominent politicians and do what you’ve always wanted to do – Whack ‘em!

Classic Mode: Hit ‘em all, and collect as many points as you can while avoiding nuclear war (don’t hit the Atomic Bomb!)

Pick-A-Party Mode: Give the opposing party a black eye or a bloody lip, but be careful you don’t hit your own candidate by mistake! Running for office is expensive, help your party collect Campaign Cash for the election!

Election Mode: Help your candidate pick up Electoral Votes to win the office, but you better hurry or your opponent will win!

Along the way, be sure to reach the Achievements, some of which include:
Finding the REAL Birth Certificate!
Dig up the tax returns and see the truth!
Whack the teleprompter and leave them tongue tied!
Collect enough Campaign Cash to run for office!

Listen to the funny things the candidates have to say as you knock them around – you’re sure to laugh out loud!

It’s time to dig out your best sneakers or cleats because wall ball is the most action-packed game of the season and it’s coming to a home town field near you! Whether you are competing on the turf or in an urban jungle, the competition is fierce and fast-paced. If you like sports and smashing your way through obstacles then wall ball will have you entertained for hours on end! Visit wallballapp.com today to sign up for the next competition!\nChoose from your favorite sports as you compete in cut-throat, wall-smashing races! There are dozens of balls that represent you as you challenge competitors and bully your way to stardom! Choose from popular favorites, like: basketball, soccer, volleyball, football, baseball, and tennis or go with some lesser-known sports, like: bowling, ping pong, cricket, golf, or billiards. If you really want to go crazy, choose from balls, like: beach balls, balloons, a golden volleyball, or marbles! For superstars that have the munchies, take your chances smashing things, like: cabbages, oranges, and apples against the brick walls! The possibilities are mind-blowing and fueled by your own imagination! Each zany ball has its own unique personality and appearance from loopy, google-eyes to an intense, athletic stare!\nOnce you decide which character you would like to represent you, it’s time to choose a field! There are many exciting walls to smash your ball against so you’ll never get bored with the scenery. Choose from bright and vivid backgrounds like a theme park or a circus. Become a hero at the local soccer field or sporting arena. Have a relaxing day near the ivy-covered brick wall or urban street. Get medieval on your enemies at the castle, or choose from several other enticing options! All of the backdrops are well-lit, brightly colored, and most importantly, really, really fun! If you have some free time on your hands, download this stunning app with irresistible characters at wallballapp.com, today!
